data.description: Looking for a spacious five-bedroom home?  Look no further!  Built in 2020, this beautiful home boasts 3009 square feet and has 2.75 baths.  The open floorplan accents the gorgeous kitchen and great room.  Granite throughout the home, finishes the kitchen and bathrooms nicely.  There is a large three car tandem garage that offers plenty of extra room for vehicles or storage.  The spacious back yard comes complete with a pergola mounted on a foundation.  This is great for enjoying the outdoors with family or friends.  Located in the fast-growing Sonoma East area, you won't want to miss this great opportunity.  Call today.
